===Noun===
#Russian monetary unit equals  one-hundredth of a [[ruble]]
===Etymology===
Russian [[копейка]] from Middle Russian kopeika, from kopie, spear (from the image of a rider with a spear on the coins minted by Moscow after the capture of Novgorod in 1478).
===Usage Note===
This is the favored spelling used by [http://themoscowtimes.com the Moscow Times]